WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.197 --> 00:00:02.135
<v Voiceover>How to use Verizon Messages.</v>

2
00:00:02.135 --> 00:00:04.713
With Verizon Messages keeping your conversations going

3
00:00:04.713 --> 00:00:06.314
has never been easier.

4
00:00:06.314 --> 00:00:08.638
Let's go over some basic Verizon messaging features

5
00:00:08.638 --> 00:00:10.357
to get you started.

6
00:00:10.357 --> 00:00:12.412
Begin by tapping the Verizon Messages icon

7
00:00:12.412 --> 00:00:16.219
from any home screen to open the app.

8
00:00:16.219 --> 00:00:18.413
To send a text message, tap the pencil icon

9
00:00:18.413 --> 00:00:21.814
in the lower right hand corner of the screen.

10
00:00:21.814 --> 00:00:23.939
Start typing the name or number of the person

11
00:00:23.939 --> 00:00:25.610
you wanna send the messages to

12
00:00:25.610 --> 00:00:27.410
and you'll see matching contacts.

13
00:00:27.410 --> 00:00:30.091
Tap the one you want.

14
00:00:30.091 --> 00:00:31.810
Addressing a message to more than one person

15
00:00:31.810 --> 00:00:35.368
will start a group conversation.

16
00:00:35.368 --> 00:00:36.674
To write your message,

17
00:00:36.674 --> 00:00:39.439
tap in the message area and start typing.

18
00:00:39.439 --> 00:00:42.970
(lighthearted music)

19
00:00:42.970 --> 00:00:47.345
When your message is complete, tap the send button.

20
00:00:47.345 --> 00:00:48.472
Responses to your text

21
00:00:48.472 --> 00:00:52.930
will be seen just below the messages you sent.

22
00:00:52.930 --> 00:00:54.172
To leave this conversation

23
00:00:54.172 --> 00:00:56.052
and the see the list of all your conversations,

24
00:00:56.052 --> 00:00:59.163
tap the back button.

25
00:00:59.163 --> 00:01:00.590
When you get a new message from someone,

26
00:01:00.590 --> 00:01:03.342
their conversation jumps to the top of the list.

27
00:01:03.342 --> 00:01:07.046
Tap the conversation to see the new message.

28
00:01:07.046 --> 00:01:08.625
Then reply by tapping the text box

29
00:01:08.625 --> 00:01:12.316
and enter in your message.

30
00:01:12.316 --> 00:01:14.528
When done, tap the send button.

31
00:01:14.528 --> 00:01:16.582
You can schedule a message to be sent at a later time

32
00:01:16.582 --> 00:01:20.087
or date, by tapping the message you want to schedule.

33
00:01:20.087 --> 00:01:23.164
Type your message, hold the send button,

34
00:01:23.164 --> 00:01:26.438
scroll up to later, choose the time and date

35
00:01:26.438 --> 00:01:31.438
for your message to be sent and tap schedule.

36
00:01:31.734 --> 00:01:36.309
To add a picture to a message, simply tap the plus button.

37
00:01:36.309 --> 00:01:38.201
Then tap gallery.

38
00:01:38.201 --> 00:01:40.605
You can attach pictures that are already on your phone

39
00:01:40.605 --> 00:01:43.657
or take a new one to share.

40
00:01:43.657 --> 00:01:48.522
Choose your photo and tap done.

41
00:01:48.522 --> 00:01:53.522
Tap the text box to add a message to go with your picture.

42
00:01:53.708 --> 00:01:57.168
When your message is complete, tap the send button.

43
00:01:57.168 --> 00:01:59.604
In addition to adding pictures to your message,

44
00:01:59.604 --> 00:02:02.601
you can use the plus sign to attach a video.

45
00:02:02.601 --> 00:02:07.601
(lighthearted music)

46
00:02:11.260 --> 00:02:13.556
Share your location through Glympse,

47
00:02:15.313 --> 00:02:16.739
give an Egift,

48
00:02:18.429 --> 00:02:20.891
create a postcard,

49
00:02:20.891 --> 00:02:25.378
add cool graphics from the internet through Media Search,

50
00:02:25.378 --> 00:02:30.195
or send someone's contact information.

51
00:02:30.195 --> 00:02:31.636
For added creativity,

52
00:02:31.636 --> 00:02:33.911
Verizon Messages lets you create a postcard

53
00:02:33.911 --> 00:02:35.827
or add personal touches to pictures

54
00:02:35.827 --> 00:02:37.811
using any combination of the collage,

55
00:02:37.811 --> 00:02:40.947
caption and sketch features.

56
00:02:40.947 --> 00:02:44.479
You can create a collage with up to five pictures.

57
00:02:44.479 --> 00:02:47.368
Pinch to resize and reposition,

58
00:02:47.368 --> 00:02:50.108
add captions and choose your fonts.

59
00:02:50.108 --> 00:02:53.696
Or use your fingers to sketch right on the image.

60
00:02:55.578 --> 00:02:58.318
You can also send an Egift card right from the app

61
00:02:58.318 --> 00:03:01.058
by choosing from over 30 merchants.

62
00:03:01.058 --> 00:03:04.387
Select your recipient,

63
00:03:04.387 --> 00:03:08.729
merchant, card art and amount you want to send

64
00:03:08.729 --> 00:03:11.814
and even add a message for that personal touch.

65
00:03:11.814 --> 00:03:13.347
You can choose to have your Egift card

66
00:03:13.347 --> 00:03:14.588
billed to your Verizon account

67
00:03:14.588 --> 00:03:16.190
or billed directly to your credit card

68
00:03:16.190 --> 00:03:20.207
by adding your credit card information here.

69
00:03:20.207 --> 00:03:21.966
Tap the menu icon in the top left corner

70
00:03:21.966 --> 00:03:25.181
of the conversation screen to get access to Driving Mode,

71
00:03:25.181 --> 00:03:26.539
Auto Reply, Settings

72
00:03:26.539 --> 00:03:29.163
and to see what's new with Verizon Messages.

73
00:03:29.163 --> 00:03:31.497
Tap to turn on or off Driving Mode.

74
00:03:31.497 --> 00:03:34.061
You can auto reply to alert recipients that you're driving

75
00:03:34.061 --> 00:03:36.302
and will get back to them later.

76
00:03:36.302 --> 00:03:38.101
You can even synch it with your car's Bluetooth

77
00:03:38.101 --> 00:03:39.845
through the settings menu

78
00:03:39.845 --> 00:03:43.422
so it automatically turns on or off.

79
00:03:43.422 --> 00:03:45.848
Integrated messaging lets you send and receive messages

80
00:03:45.848 --> 00:03:48.669
on your tablet and computer, in addition to your phone.

81
00:03:48.669 --> 00:03:51.408
Use the settings menu to manage this feature.

82
00:03:51.408 --> 00:03:52.628
These are just a few of the ways

83
00:03:52.628 --> 00:03:55.844
Verizon Messages makes texting easy and fun.

84
00:03:55.844 --> 00:03:57.527
To learn more about Verizon Messages,

85
00:03:57.527 --> 00:03:59.581
please visit Verizon wireless dot com

86
00:03:59.581 --> 00:04:02.420
slash Verizon messages.

